# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok in simultaneous attacks on israeli tourists in kenya , a car bomb exploded at an israeli-owned hotel on thursday , killing ## people , and at least two missiles were fired at _ but missed _ an israeli airliner .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (e / explode-01
            :ARG1 (b / bomb
                  :mod (c / car))
            :location (h / hotel
                  :ARG1-of (o / own-01
                        :ARG0 (c2 / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Israel"))))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday))
            :ARG0-of (k / kill-01
                  :ARG1 (p / person)))
      :op2 (f / fire-01
            :ARG1 (m / missile
                  :quant (a2 / at-least
                        :op1 2))
            :direction (a3 / airliner
                  :mod c2)
            :ARG1-of (c3 / contrast-01
                  :ARG2 (m2 / miss-02
                        :ARG0 m
                        :ARG1 a3)))
      :subevent-of (a4 / attack-01
            :ARG1 (p2 / person
                  :mod c2
                  :ARG0-of (t2 / tour-01))
            :mod (s / simultaneous)
            :location c2
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Kenya")))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok after a two-year legal drama , a baltimore district judge dismissed a creditors ' lawsuit against host marriott corp. that charged the company and its highest-ranking officials with securities fraud .
# ::alignments
(d / dismiss-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG3 (j / judge-01))
            :location (c / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Baltimore"))
            :mod (d2 / district))
      :ARG1 (s / sue-02
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c2 / company
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Marriott"
                                    :op2 "Corp.")
                              :ARG0-of (h3 / host-01))
                        :ARG2 (o / official
                              :ARG1-of (r / rank-01
                                    :ARG2 (h4 / high-02
                                          :ARG2-of (h5 / have-degree-91
                                                :ARG1 r
                                                :ARG3 (m / most)))))))
            :ARG1 c2
            :ARG2 (d3 / defraud-01
                  :ARG0 c2
                  :ARG1 (s2 / securities)))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (d4 / drama
                  :ARG1-of (l / legal-02)
                  :duration (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 2
                        :unit (y / year)))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok kim kum sok won the first gold medal for dpr korea at the ##th guangzhou asian games as he won the men 's ##kg weightlifting here on monday .
# ::alignments
(w / win-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Kim"
                  :op2 "Kum"
                  :op3 "Sok"))
      :ARG1 (m / medal
            :mod (g / gold)
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1))
      :ARG4 (c / country
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "DPR")
            :mod (c2 / country
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Korea")))
      :time (g2 / game
            :location (c3 / city
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Guangzhou")
                  :mod (c4 / continent
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Asia"))))
      :ARG1-of (c5 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (w2 / win-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (w3 / weightlift-01
                        :ARG0 (m2 / man)
                        :ARG1 (m3 / mass-quantity
                              :quant 55
                              :unit (k / kilogram)))
                  :location (h / here)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (m4 / monday)))))

                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))

            :ARG1 (r / record
                  :quant 2
                  :mod (w2 / world))

            :ARG1-of (m / mean-01
                  :ARG2 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (r2 / record
                              :quant 1
                              :topic (a3 / altitude))
                        :op2 (r3 / record
                              :quant 1
                              :topic (l / level
                                    :mod (s3 / sea))))))
      :location (h2 / here)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02)
                  :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)))

            :weekday (w / wednesday))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (d2 / defeat-01
                  :ARG0 (p3 / political-party
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "socialism")

                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (m / margin
                        :ARG1-of (w2 / wide-02))
                  :time (e / elect-01
                        :ARG1-of (g / general-02)
                        :time (w3 / weekend)))))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / committee
            :mod (ii / international)
            :mod (o / organization
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Red"
                        :op2 "Cross")))
      :ARG1 (l / leave-11
            :ARG0 (c2 / convoy
                  :mod (t / truck))
            :ARG1 (c3 / city
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Kabul"))
            :ARG2 (c4 / carry-01
                  :ARG0 c2
                  :ARG1 (f / food
                        :beneficiary (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (r / reside-01
                                    :ARG1 c3
                                    :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                                          :ARG1 (c5 / country
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Afghanistan"))
                                          :ARG2 (c6 / capital)))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday)))

# ::tok top bosnian serb official momcilo krajisnik on sunday told pope john paul ii in sarajevo that war criminals in the former yugoslavia should be pardoned , the serbs ' beta news agency reported .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (a / agency
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "beta")
            :mod (n2 / news)
            :poss (p / person
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Scotland"))))
      :ARG1 (t / tell-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Santorum")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c2 / country
                              :name (n5 / name
                                    :op1 "Bosnia"))
                        :ARG2 (o / official))
                  :mod (t2 / top))
            :ARG1 (r2 / recommend-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / pardon-01
                        :ARG1 (p4 / person
                              :ARG2-of (c3 / criminal-03
                                    :mod (w / war))
                              :location (c4 / country
                                    :name (n6 / name
                                          :op1 "Yugoslavia")
                                    :time (f / former)))))
            :ARG2 (p5 / person
                  :name (n7 / name
                        :op1 "John"
                        :op2 "Paul"
                        :op3 "II")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 c
                        :ARG2 (p6 / pope)))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (s / sunday))))
